Mangalore Refinery Offers 111,000 Tons of Oil Products in July

-- B y   Y e e   K a i   P i n
-- 
2011-05-30T00:41:57Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-30/mangalore-refinery-offers-111-000-tons-of-oil-products-in-july.html
India ’s  Mangalore Refinery &
Petrochemicals Ltd. (MRPL)  offered to sell 111,000 metric tons of oil
products for loading in July, the company said in documents e-
mailed to potential buyers.  Oil & Natural Gas Corp., the country’s largest oil
producer, owns 72 percent of Mangalore Refinery.  Details of the offers are as follow:  To contact the reporter on this story:
